Package: pgtde-@PG_MAJOR@
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser, tzdata, ssl-cert
Description: Percona PostgreSQL @PG_VERSION@ kernel with TDE-aware tools
 This package ships Percona Server for PostgreSQL @PG_VERSION@.@PERCONA_RELEASE@
 under /usr/pgtde-@PG_MAJOR@. It includes the server, client tools, headers,
 PGXS files, procedural languages, bundled contrib extensions, and TDE-aware
 PostgreSQL utilities exposed under their canonical pg_* names.

Package: pgtde-@PG_MAJOR@-contrib
Architecture: any
Depends: pgtde-@PG_MAJOR@ (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: pg-tde (= @PGTDE_VERSION@)
Description: pg_tde @PGTDE_VERSION@ extension for pgtde-@PG_MAJOR@
 This package provides the pg_tde transparent data encryption extension,
 its SQL files, and TDE-specific operational helpers for the private
 /usr/pgtde-@PG_MAJOR@ PostgreSQL installation.
